@wp.kernel

    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = (v1 / (0.91 / 0.66))
    tmp = tmp
    v1 = v1
    v2 = ((wp.cos(v2 + 0.69) * wp.sin(v1 + 0.08)) * wp.exp(0.73))
    v0 = v1
    data[tid] = v0
